1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,289 --> 00:01:44,039
[Love Never Fails]
[EP18]

3
00:02:07,130 --> 00:02:08,800
Hongning, Bailing, Lujiu...

4
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:10,120
All three are missing.

5
00:02:11,830 --> 00:02:12,990
When were they

6
00:02:13,250 --> 00:02:14,130
last seen?

7
00:02:14,610 --> 00:02:15,930
I saw them head to the back mountain.

8
00:02:16,210 --> 00:02:17,130
Haven't seen them since.

9
00:02:17,770 --> 00:02:18,730
I checked the whole back mountain.

10
00:02:18,890 --> 00:02:19,810
No sign of them.

11
00:02:20,170 --> 00:02:21,050
It's way past curfew,

12
00:02:21,410 --> 00:02:22,450
they're still not back.

13
00:02:27,170 --> 00:02:27,690
I wonder

14
00:02:27,770 --> 00:02:29,570
how Lujiu is doing.

15
00:02:31,050 --> 00:02:32,170
Worrying won't fix anything.

16
00:02:33,250 --> 00:02:34,290
Even Lujiu

17
00:02:34,530 --> 00:02:35,610
couldn't handle that demon.

18
00:02:36,050 --> 00:02:37,650
You'd just get in the way.

19
00:02:38,890 --> 00:02:40,250
Let's make a plan first.

20
00:02:40,970 --> 00:02:42,290
You've got a point.

21
00:02:42,930 --> 00:02:44,610
I've set up protective barriers here.

22
00:02:45,090 --> 00:02:46,370
Even a powerful demon

23
00:02:46,810 --> 00:02:47,930
couldn't break through easily.

24
00:02:48,650 --> 00:02:49,210
Tonight

25
00:02:49,890 --> 00:02:51,650
we'll take a rest here.

26
00:02:52,090 --> 00:02:54,730
Everyone says you can always

27
00:02:55,010 --> 00:02:55,770
stay calm in a crisis

28
00:02:56,010 --> 00:02:56,770
and deal with

29
00:02:56,930 --> 00:02:57,690
evil monsters.

30
00:02:58,410 --> 00:02:59,490
You really live up to the hype!

31
00:03:00,890 --> 00:03:01,970
I slew demons

32
00:03:02,290 --> 00:03:03,890
during my travels.

33
00:03:04,050 --> 00:03:06,290
They lack moral codes,

34
00:03:06,770 --> 00:03:07,770
born wild by nature.

35
00:03:08,730 --> 00:03:09,690
One misstep,

36
00:03:09,930 --> 00:03:11,330
they stray from the path,

37
00:03:11,490 --> 00:03:12,410
committing wicked deeds.

38
00:03:13,170 --> 00:03:14,570
As a cultivator,

39
00:03:14,730 --> 00:03:16,410
I must stop them.

40
00:03:17,370 --> 00:03:18,090
That's why

41
00:03:18,490 --> 00:03:20,810
I don't get why Cangwu Academy

42
00:03:20,970 --> 00:03:22,290
admit pixie disciples.

43
00:03:22,730 --> 00:03:23,850
It should

44
00:03:24,050 --> 00:03:25,329
set a good example

45
00:03:26,250 --> 00:03:28,370
for all cultivators.

46
00:03:29,210 --> 00:03:30,050
Yet ignoring

47
00:03:30,250 --> 00:03:30,970
the natural divide

48
00:03:31,050 --> 00:03:32,530
between humans and demons,

49
00:03:32,730 --> 00:03:33,770
it allows pixies

50
00:03:34,250 --> 00:03:35,610
to practice cultivation.

51
00:03:44,570 --> 00:03:45,090
Wait,

52
00:03:45,810 --> 00:03:47,490
why can't pixies do that?

53
00:03:48,210 --> 00:03:49,730
Actually, all can.

54
00:03:50,170 --> 00:03:51,170
Pixies, spirits,

55
00:03:51,290 --> 00:03:53,250
mortals and immortals...

56
00:03:53,610 --> 00:03:54,930
But pixies'

57
00:03:55,770 --> 00:03:57,650
wild instincts

58
00:03:58,050 --> 00:04:00,450
make most turn bad.

59
00:04:00,730 --> 00:04:03,530
The Academy breaks rules

60
00:04:03,890 --> 00:04:05,130
by teaching them.

61
00:04:06,490 --> 00:04:07,410
Why do you talk like that?

62
00:04:07,490 --> 00:04:08,610
It's so off-putting!

63
00:04:10,650 --> 00:04:12,290
Pixies aren't born evil!

64
00:04:12,810 --> 00:04:13,690
That's just bias.

65
00:04:13,970 --> 00:04:15,250
I grew up around pixies.

66
00:04:15,570 --> 00:04:17,010
I've dealt with many,

67
00:04:17,329 --> 00:04:19,010
and plenty are kind-hearted.

68
00:04:20,010 --> 00:04:20,529
Please tell me,

69
00:04:21,490 --> 00:04:23,250
have you had the pixie-sensing ability

70
00:04:23,730 --> 00:04:24,930
since childhood?

71
00:04:25,370 --> 00:04:25,850
Yeah.

72
00:04:27,610 --> 00:04:28,770
Never failed?

73
00:04:31,050 --> 00:04:32,330
Not once by now.

74
00:04:33,130 --> 00:04:34,130
My apologies.

75
00:04:34,730 --> 00:04:36,730
I forgot you grew up among pixies.

76
00:04:37,730 --> 00:04:39,130
I've been narrow-minded.

77
00:04:41,890 --> 00:04:43,409
Your fight against evil

78
00:04:43,730 --> 00:04:45,409
is truly admirable.

79
00:04:47,570 --> 00:04:49,250
But while mortals fear pixies,

80
00:04:49,690 --> 00:04:51,490
pixies too fear mortals.

81
00:04:52,890 --> 00:04:55,330
So there's not much difference.

82
00:05:44,890 --> 00:05:46,170
You still haven't told me

83
00:05:46,570 --> 00:05:47,810
why you argued with Master.

84
00:05:50,050 --> 00:05:51,050
We didn't argue.

85
00:05:51,610 --> 00:05:52,810
You know,

86
00:05:53,450 --> 00:05:55,330
he always beats around the bush,

87
00:05:55,770 --> 00:05:57,890
acting hot and cold sometimes.

88
00:05:58,290 --> 00:05:59,170
I'm pretty sure

89
00:05:59,290 --> 00:06:00,890
he's the immortal I met as a kid.

90
00:06:01,010 --> 00:06:02,090
But he keeps denying it.

91
00:06:04,610 --> 00:06:05,650
He seems

92
00:06:05,810 --> 00:06:07,210
all warm and kind,

93
00:06:08,050 --> 00:06:09,490
but turns frosty

94
00:06:09,890 --> 00:06:11,210
the moment you get close.

95
00:06:13,650 --> 00:06:14,730
Finally, someone gets it!

96
00:06:15,210 --> 00:06:16,490
I only dare drop hints about him—

97
00:06:16,570 --> 00:06:17,450
never say it outright.

98
00:06:18,770 --> 00:06:19,490
Isn't he

99
00:06:19,650 --> 00:06:22,290
like a brick wall?

100
00:06:22,610 --> 00:06:23,650
Bottles up every thought,

101
00:06:24,050 --> 00:06:25,930
makes us play guessing games—

102
00:06:26,770 --> 00:06:28,250
cold as an iceberg, right?

103
00:06:28,650 --> 00:06:29,530
Bailing...

104
00:06:30,130 --> 00:06:31,890
He's always been kind to you.

105
00:06:32,050 --> 00:06:33,730
How can you trash-talk him?

106
00:06:34,050 --> 00:06:35,170
How could you?

107
00:06:36,570 --> 00:06:37,130
What?

108
00:06:38,330 --> 00:06:39,890
Are you for real?

109
00:06:40,010 --> 00:06:40,690
I was just…

110
00:06:41,730 --> 00:06:43,330
agreeing with you!

111
00:06:43,330 --> 00:06:44,850
I can make judgments.

112
00:06:45,210 --> 00:06:46,890
But your words...

113
00:06:47,250 --> 00:06:48,409
did make me furious!

114
00:06:54,570 --> 00:06:55,010
Fine!

115
00:06:55,330 --> 00:06:56,250
Fine, fine!

116
00:06:56,530 --> 00:06:56,970
Okay!

117
00:06:57,050 --> 00:06:57,530
My bad.

118
00:06:57,610 --> 00:06:58,370
I shouldn't have said that.

119
00:06:58,970 --> 00:06:59,490
Happy now?

120
00:06:59,970 --> 00:07:00,650
Fine.

121
00:07:05,090 --> 00:07:06,610
Wonder how Lujiu

122
00:07:06,930 --> 00:07:08,010
is doing though.

123
00:07:10,050 --> 00:07:10,730
Relax.

124
00:07:11,170 --> 00:07:12,810
He's cunning.

125
00:07:12,970 --> 00:07:14,130
He'll save his own hide.

126
00:07:15,330 --> 00:07:17,130
That's stereotyping.

127
00:07:17,770 --> 00:07:20,850
Lujiu is actually genuine.

128
00:07:26,490 --> 00:07:27,450
Got an idea!

129
00:07:40,970 --> 00:07:42,090
See? He's fine.

130
00:07:42,330 --> 00:07:43,050
What's this?

131
00:07:43,850 --> 00:07:45,409
This is Life Smoke.

132
00:07:45,730 --> 00:07:47,090
It can track souls.

133
00:07:47,530 --> 00:07:48,370
See these three blazing branches?

134
00:07:48,490 --> 00:07:49,650
Flames this strong mean

135
00:07:50,010 --> 00:07:51,450
he's alive and kicking!

136
00:07:51,770 --> 00:07:53,610
Why not use this earlier?

137
00:07:54,450 --> 00:07:54,890
I...

138
00:07:55,130 --> 00:07:55,930
I just...

139
00:07:56,250 --> 00:07:58,330
don't get to use charms much!

140
00:07:59,170 --> 00:08:00,130
Enough worrying.

141
00:08:00,730 --> 00:08:01,810
Can we finally get some sleep?

142
00:08:37,970 --> 00:08:38,490
Master!

143
00:08:40,770 --> 00:08:41,330
How's going?

144
00:08:41,530 --> 00:08:42,530
Any updates?

145
00:08:42,809 --> 00:08:43,850
Not yet.

146
00:08:45,930 --> 00:08:47,090
Secure the Academy.

147
00:08:47,250 --> 00:08:47,770
I'll search for them.

148
00:08:47,970 --> 00:08:48,730
But your injuries…

149
00:08:48,890 --> 00:08:49,570
Manageable.

150
00:08:49,930 --> 00:08:50,610
If they return,

151
00:08:50,730 --> 00:08:51,570
notify me immediately.

152
00:08:51,730 --> 00:08:52,210
Understood.

153
00:08:53,650 --> 00:08:54,410
Be careful, Master.

154
00:09:14,570 --> 00:09:15,170
[What's wrong?]

155
00:09:15,690 --> 00:09:16,330
[What's going on?]

156
00:09:16,650 --> 00:09:17,730
[They are missing!]

157
00:09:17,890 --> 00:09:18,410
[What?]

158
00:09:18,970 --> 00:09:19,690
[They're gone?]

159
00:09:20,090 --> 00:09:20,770
[Search everywhere!]

160
00:09:20,930 --> 00:09:21,650
[Check over there!]

161
00:09:22,050 --> 00:09:22,450
[They're missing!]

162
00:09:22,570 --> 00:09:23,250
What's happening here?

163
00:09:23,810 --> 00:09:25,250
Some are missing.

164
00:09:25,410 --> 00:09:26,370
Master ordered a full search.

165
00:09:26,490 --> 00:09:27,170
Who's missing?

166
00:09:27,290 --> 00:09:27,850
Lujiu,

167
00:09:28,010 --> 00:09:28,730
Bailing,

168
00:09:28,890 --> 00:09:29,450
and Hongning.

169
00:09:29,570 --> 00:09:30,170
[Nothing here.]

170
00:09:30,930 --> 00:09:31,410
[Hello?]

171
00:09:44,130 --> 00:09:45,370
By the Floral Deity's power,

172
00:09:45,770 --> 00:09:46,930
summon the Floral Spirit.

173
00:09:57,050 --> 00:09:58,490
[No trace of Hongning,]

174
00:09:58,810 --> 00:09:59,930
[Bailing,]

175
00:10:00,530 --> 00:10:01,610
[or Lujiu.]

176
00:10:17,090 --> 00:10:17,850
Where are you going?

177
00:10:18,130 --> 00:10:18,730
I'll join you.

178
00:10:19,370 --> 00:10:20,650
This is my responsibility.

179
00:10:20,890 --> 00:10:21,730
Stay calm.

180
00:10:21,890 --> 00:10:23,090
I'll handle it.

181
00:10:24,930 --> 00:10:26,130
Don't overthink.

182
00:10:26,410 --> 00:10:27,890
I'm here for Lujiu and Bailing.

183
00:10:28,730 --> 00:10:30,090
Don't slow me down.

184
00:10:43,090 --> 00:10:43,690
Excuse me,

185
00:10:44,170 --> 00:10:45,890
how far is Cangwu Academy?

186
00:10:47,130 --> 00:10:48,850
There's a Dragon Abyss ahead.

187
00:10:49,410 --> 00:10:50,170
Circle around it,

188
00:10:50,290 --> 00:10:51,650
take the mountain path upward,

189
00:10:51,850 --> 00:10:52,570
and you'll arrive.

190
00:10:53,450 --> 00:10:54,170
Thanks.

191
00:10:55,250 --> 00:10:55,810
Wait.

192
00:10:56,650 --> 00:10:58,490
You seem like a traveler.

193
00:10:59,090 --> 00:11:00,610
That abyss houses

194
00:11:01,250 --> 00:11:02,450
a demonic dragon!

195
00:11:03,010 --> 00:11:04,730
Don't take shortcuts

196
00:11:04,890 --> 00:11:05,930
through it,

197
00:11:06,450 --> 00:11:08,570
make sure to go around!

198
00:11:08,970 --> 00:11:09,650
Demon?

199
00:11:14,250 --> 00:11:15,690
Remember to stay cautious

200
00:11:15,810 --> 00:11:17,050
around strangers.

201
00:11:17,450 --> 00:11:18,850
Don't naively

202
00:11:19,170 --> 00:11:20,370
trust everyone's good.

203
00:11:20,650 --> 00:11:21,330
Demon!

204
00:11:21,730 --> 00:11:22,730
Help!

205
00:11:26,850 --> 00:11:28,650
Why not kill him?

206
00:11:29,890 --> 00:11:30,650
Too messy.

207
00:11:31,970 --> 00:11:32,490
Oh,

208
00:11:33,010 --> 00:11:34,170
do you known that

209
00:11:34,650 --> 00:11:36,250
the camellia pixie became mortal?

210
00:11:36,570 --> 00:11:37,730
She's forgotten you completely.

211
00:11:40,570 --> 00:11:42,130
I'll make her remember.

212
00:12:01,850 --> 00:12:02,890
Remember how to activate

213
00:12:03,370 --> 00:12:03,970
the Demon-Binding Curse?

214
00:12:05,130 --> 00:12:06,170
Of course I do.

215
00:12:08,730 --> 00:12:09,610
Vanquish demons,

216
00:12:10,090 --> 00:12:11,130
purge evil spirits—

217
00:12:11,490 --> 00:12:12,530
by Divine Decree.

218
00:12:20,210 --> 00:12:20,810
I'm sorry!

219
00:12:21,290 --> 00:12:22,130
Let me help you!

220
00:12:23,770 --> 00:12:25,290
You got the curse right,

221
00:12:25,410 --> 00:12:26,410
but stop aiming at me!

222
00:12:26,610 --> 00:12:27,770
I'm technically demon-kind too!

223
00:12:27,930 --> 00:12:28,490
Sorry! My bad!

224
00:12:28,730 --> 00:12:29,170
Guys,

225
00:12:29,610 --> 00:12:30,570
the demon miasma's cleared.

226
00:12:31,090 --> 00:12:32,330
Time to move out.

227
00:12:37,290 --> 00:12:38,050
Come on!

228
00:12:38,850 --> 00:12:39,330
Hurry up!

229
00:12:43,210 --> 00:12:44,690
Since I'm helping your search,

230
00:12:45,050 --> 00:12:45,730
do you two

231
00:12:45,890 --> 00:12:47,210
have any leads to share?

232
00:12:48,090 --> 00:12:49,170
Last night I heard

233
00:12:49,370 --> 00:12:50,370
you mention

234
00:12:50,650 --> 00:12:51,650
"Lujiu"?

235
00:12:52,410 --> 00:12:52,810
Right.

236
00:12:53,170 --> 00:12:54,210
He's fox clan.

237
00:12:54,370 --> 00:12:54,930
Fox?

238
00:12:55,970 --> 00:12:57,410
Does he wield Spiritual Flame?

239
00:12:57,810 --> 00:12:58,730
How'd you know?

240
00:12:59,090 --> 00:13:00,170
On my way here,

241
00:13:00,490 --> 00:13:02,450
I saw a scorched stone tablet.

242
00:13:02,850 --> 00:13:03,410
Could that be

243
00:13:03,610 --> 00:13:05,130
a clue left

244
00:13:05,290 --> 00:13:06,410
by Lujiu?

245
00:13:07,130 --> 00:13:08,130
Where's the tablet?

246
00:13:08,370 --> 00:13:09,290
What's carved on it?

247
00:13:10,210 --> 00:13:11,330
"To Dragon Abyss".

248
00:13:12,250 --> 00:13:13,010
Dragon Abyss?

249
00:13:14,210 --> 00:13:15,330
Where's that?

250
00:13:16,490 --> 00:13:17,370
That's a place

251
00:13:17,490 --> 00:13:18,410
every Cangwu disciple knows.

252
00:13:33,090 --> 00:13:34,170
This path leads to Dragon Abyss.

253
00:13:34,490 --> 00:13:35,170
The trip's treacherous.

254
00:13:35,610 --> 00:13:36,610
I'll go alone.

255
00:13:37,290 --> 00:13:38,690
Please search the right path.

256
00:13:38,930 --> 00:13:39,770
If nothing's found,

257
00:13:39,930 --> 00:13:41,130
regroup at the academy.

258
00:13:41,330 --> 00:13:41,770
Understood.

259
00:13:42,130 --> 00:13:42,690
Take care.

260
00:13:57,570 --> 00:13:59,250
The demonic aura here's so dense.

261
00:14:00,210 --> 00:14:01,690
It feels amazing.

262
00:14:06,570 --> 00:14:07,250
Baicha,

263
00:14:07,770 --> 00:14:08,810
you've been staring forever.

264
00:14:08,810 --> 00:14:09,890
What exactly are you looking at?

265
00:14:10,770 --> 00:14:11,930
I was figuring out where to enter.

266
00:14:12,690 --> 00:14:13,490
Enter?

267
00:14:14,170 --> 00:14:14,930
Are you insane?

268
00:14:15,410 --> 00:14:16,490
Didn't you hear that?

269
00:14:16,690 --> 00:14:18,250
A demonic dragon lurks below!

270
00:14:18,890 --> 00:14:20,570
This place traps the dragon

271
00:14:20,970 --> 00:14:22,370
'cause below lies a forbidden zone—

272
00:14:22,490 --> 00:14:23,410
the Yin Spring,

273
00:14:23,690 --> 00:14:25,130
requiring demonic force to balance it.

274
00:14:25,490 --> 00:14:26,690
What's the Yin Spring?

275
00:14:29,610 --> 00:14:30,450
Waters that awaken

276
00:14:30,570 --> 00:14:31,810
memories of past lives.

277
00:14:32,130 --> 00:14:34,210
You want her to remember you?

278
00:14:36,370 --> 00:14:37,090
Enough talk.

279
00:14:37,610 --> 00:14:38,370
Follow me down.

280
00:14:38,770 --> 00:14:39,250
But...

281
00:14:39,450 --> 00:14:40,090
I... eh...

282
00:14:40,210 --> 00:14:41,050
I'll just stay here.

283
00:14:41,170 --> 00:14:41,690
I'd rather...

284
00:14:43,290 --> 00:14:44,130
Baicha!

285
00:14:44,410 --> 00:14:45,290
No!

286
00:14:48,290 --> 00:14:48,810
Ma'am,

287
00:14:49,650 --> 00:14:51,130
if Lujiu's truly trapped in Dragon Abyss,

288
00:14:51,330 --> 00:14:52,090
this is way beyond

289
00:14:52,210 --> 00:14:53,170
what we can handle.

290
00:14:54,010 --> 00:14:54,890
I'm gonna take her back.

291
00:14:55,090 --> 00:14:55,970
We should report to Master.

292
00:14:56,530 --> 00:14:57,490
I'm not leaving!

293
00:14:58,490 --> 00:14:59,770
Stop being stubborn!

294
00:15:00,130 --> 00:15:01,450
If even Lujiu couldn't

295
00:15:01,610 --> 00:15:02,650
handle that dragon,

296
00:15:02,890 --> 00:15:03,290
we'd just be

297
00:15:03,450 --> 00:15:04,450
snack-sized offerings for it!

298
00:15:05,930 --> 00:15:07,050
My pixie-sensing ability

299
00:15:07,650 --> 00:15:08,650
might help.

300
00:15:08,930 --> 00:15:09,450
Besides,

301
