394
00:18:47,250 --> 00:18:48,250
[In my weakened state,]

395
00:18:48,970 --> 00:18:50,410
[direct confrontation's unwise.]

396
00:18:58,690 --> 00:18:59,250
Hongning,

397
00:18:59,930 --> 00:19:01,010
