pixie-sensing gift?

400
00:19:06,690 --> 00:19:07,810
I was born with it.

401
00:19:08,210 --> 00:19:09,490
As a kid, I communicated

402
00:19:09,650 --> 00:19:10,810
with cats and dogs,

403
00:19:11,090 --> 00:19:12,090
freaking everyone out.

404
00:19:12,490 --> 00:19:13,370
Later, I learned

405
00:19:13,730 --> 00:19:15,010
only I could see their true forms.

406
00:19:16,730 --> 00:19:17,650
This ability

407
00:19:18,170 --> 00:19:20,930
might be heaven's gift.

408
00:19:22,890 --> 00:19:23,770
Gift?

409
00:19:24,730 --> 00:19:26,450
Yes.

410
00:19:27,130 --> 00:19:30,010
And with it comes duty

411
00:19:30,330 --> 00:19:31,690
to wield it wisely.

412
00:19:33,050 --> 00:19:34,730
I don't follow.

413
00:19:36,650 --> 00:19:38,130
In centuries of demon-slaying,

414
00:19:38,890 --> 00:19:40,090
I've eliminated

415
00:19:40,410 --> 00:19:41,530
mere hundreds.

416
00:19:42,530 --> 00:19:44,450
If I had your ability,

417
00:19:45,090 --> 00:19:46,050
I could

418
00:19:46,530 --> 00:19:48,370
purge all pixies and demons

419
00:19:48,610 --> 00:19:49,970
from this world!

420
00:19:51,570 --> 00:19:52,170
Ma'am,

421
00:19:52,770 --> 00:19:53,770
to eliminate evil,

422
00:19:53,970 --> 00:19:55,650
you need to base your actions

423
00:19:56,130 --> 00:19:56,850
on what they've done,

424
00:19:57,010 --> 00:19:58,770
not their origins.

425
00:19:58,970 --> 00:20:00,090
Killing pixies or demons

426
