470
00:21:45,410 --> 00:21:46,730
There's no stele at all.

471
00:21:47,130 --> 00:21:48,410
You tricked me into coming here.

472
00:21:50,850 --> 00:21:52,570
So all your obedience just now

473
00:21:52,770 --> 00:21:54,090
was just an act.

474
00:21:55,010 --> 00:21:56,050
Then tell me,

475
00:21:57,010 --> 00:21:58,850
why do you think I brought you here?

476
00:22:00,210 --> 00:22:01,930
You wanted to confirm something.

477
00:22:02,410 --> 00:22:03,490
I'll just give you the answer.

478
00:22:05,090 --> 00:22:06,930
You're a demon, not an immortal.

479
00:22:07,170 --> 00:22:07,690
Shut up!

480
00:22:08,290 --> 00:22:08,890
Don't think

481
00:22:09,050 --> 00:22:10,210
I won't deal with you just 'cause

482
00:22:10,330 --> 00:22:11,290
you're from Cangwu Academy.

483
00:22:11,570 --> 00:22:12,450
But that's the truth.

484
00:22:12,850 --> 00:22:13,810
I knew what you were

485
00:22:13,970 --> 00:22:14,970
the moment I saw you.

486
00:22:15,290 --> 00:22:16,810
You're the demon that rabbit spirit

487
00:22:16,970 --> 00:22:17,570
was talking about.

488
00:22:17,930 --> 00:22:18,610
[A demon!]

489
00:22:19,290 --> 00:22:20,210
[Over there!]

490
00:22:22,650 --> 00:22:23,170
No!

491
00:22:23,290 --> 00:22:24,010
I'm not a demon!

492
00:22:27,450 --> 00:22:27,930
You...

493
00:22:28,450 --> 00:22:29,410
You side with demons

494
00:22:29,570 --> 00:22:30,490
and defend them.

495
00:22:31,570 --> 00:22:33,410
I'm just a mortal girl.

496
00:22:33,650 --> 00:22:35,370
Don't you think you sound ridiculous?

497
00:22:36,490 --> 00:22:38,130
You really think you can wait

498
00:22:38,370 --> 00:22:39,770
for your master to save you?

499
00:22:40,130 --> 00:22:41,170
I'll capture you now.

500
00:22:41,370 --> 00:22:43,050
And kill Bailing then.

501
00:22:43,170 --> 00:22:44,290
You...

502
00:22:44,450 --> 00:22:45,690
What can you get from catching me?

503
00:22:45,930 --> 00:22:47,050
You gonna rip out my eyes

504
00:22:47,290 --> 00:22:48,410
