505
00:22:48,930 --> 00:22:49,730
Maybe to others

506
00:22:49,970 --> 00:22:51,850
you're a fairy from the North Sea,

507
00:22:52,410 --> 00:22:53,370
but to me,

508
00:22:53,730 --> 00:22:54,690
you're just a self-deceiving demon

509
00:22:54,850 --> 00:22:55,930
that can't tell right from wrong.

510
00:22:56,330 --> 00:22:58,090
Enough! Shut up!

511
00:23:20,490 --> 00:23:21,130
Master.

512
00:23:22,530 --> 00:23:23,330
I thought

513
00:23:23,890 --> 00:23:25,570
I was hallucinating.

514
00:23:26,530 --> 00:23:27,450
It's really you.

515
00:23:29,170 --> 00:23:29,970
Where are we?

516
00:23:30,890 --> 00:23:31,890
This is the Dragon Abyss.

517
00:23:32,090 --> 00:23:33,050
You've gone for so long.

518
00:23:33,370 --> 00:23:34,290
What happened?

519
00:23:35,970 --> 00:23:37,050
Long story.

520
00:23:37,810 --> 00:23:39,690
We heard Lujiu was being held here,

521
00:23:39,970 --> 00:23:41,050
so we followed the trail.

522
00:23:41,290 --> 00:23:42,690
We then ran into Master Dongxuan.

523
00:23:42,850 --> 00:23:43,370
Where's Bailing?

524
00:23:43,930 --> 00:23:45,250
He went back to Cangwu to find you.

525
00:23:49,210 --> 00:23:50,250
This is the Sorrow Devouring Tree.

526
00:23:50,810 --> 00:23:52,010
It feeds on pain,

527
00:23:54,730 --> 00:23:56,290
drains your spirit,

528
00:23:56,890 --> 00:23:58,290
and lures you into eating its fruit.

529
00:23:58,970 --> 00:24:01,690
Once you do, you become part of it.

530
00:24:06,250 --> 00:24:07,690
No, it's the Mind Bending Sound.

531
00:24:10,010 --> 00:24:10,530
Don't listen to it!

532
00:24:11,170 --> 00:24:12,050
Recite the Serenity Litany.

533
00:24:12,690 --> 00:24:13,850
Serenity Litany?

534
00:24:16,010 --> 00:24:18,170
Still your heart, curb your desires.

535
00:24:20,570 --> 00:24:21,090
Master!

536
00:24:21,530 --> 00:24:22,490
Are you okay?

537
00:24:23,050 --> 00:24:24,050
Recite the litany too.

538
00:24:24,250 --> 00:24:25,530
Still your heart, curb your desires.

539
00:24:25,810 --> 00:24:26,290
Master!

540
00:24:52,690 --> 00:24:54,050
As long as I eat the fruit,

541
00:24:56,090 --> 00:24:56,970
I can finally

542
00:24:57,410 --> 00:24:59,690
be free from the endless pain.

543
00:25:48,690 --> 00:25:49,490
I don't know

544
00:25:50,770 --> 00:25:52,730
