545
00:26:09,050 --> 00:26:09,690
Master,

546
00:26:10,490 --> 00:26:11,290
don't run from it.

547
00:26:11,930 --> 00:26:12,810
The only way out

548
00:26:13,210 --> 00:26:14,330
is to face it.

549
00:26:36,970 --> 00:26:37,490
Master!

550
00:26:38,410 --> 00:26:39,370
You're awake?

551
00:26:40,610 --> 00:26:41,650
This place is dangerous.

552
00:26:42,010 --> 00:26:43,730
The Tree won't give up

553
00:26:43,930 --> 00:26:45,010
