554
00:26:45,290 --> 00:26:45,930
We need to leave now.

555
00:26:46,650 --> 00:26:47,010
Let's go.

556
00:26:47,210 --> 00:26:47,610
Go.

557
00:27:09,010 --> 00:27:09,730
What are you doing here?

558
00:27:10,090 --> 00:27:11,050
I should be asking you that.

559
00:27:12,650 --> 00:27:15,530
Hongning and I were looking for Lujiu.

560
00:27:16,250 --> 00:27:17,250
There are some leads.

561
00:27:17,450 --> 00:27:18,410
I planned to return to report.

562
00:27:18,890 --> 00:27:20,610
But I felt something was off on the way,

563
00:27:21,330 --> 00:27:22,210
so I came back for Hongning.

564
00:27:22,690 --> 00:27:23,490
But she's missing too.

565
00:27:26,530 --> 00:27:27,370
Don't tell me

566
00:27:27,530 --> 00:27:28,690
you're here for Lujiu too?

567
00:27:28,930 --> 00:27:29,770
Don't waste my time.

568
00:27:32,850 --> 00:27:33,730
Tell me,

569
00:27:33,930 --> 00:27:35,210
what exactly is going on between you two?

570
00:27:35,570 --> 00:27:36,490
This is what you care about

571
00:27:36,770 --> 00:27:37,370
